
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pneumothorax' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Apical pneumothorax' radio button is enabled
And 'Coat formed pneumothorax' radio button is enabled
And 'Seropneumothorax' radio button is enabled
And 'Narrow' radio button is enabled
And 'Marked' radio button is enabled
And 'Subtotal' radio button is enabled
And 'Max. width' input field is enabled

And 'Mediastinal shift' checkbox is enabled
And 'Atelectasis' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Mediastinal shift' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled 
